Full Description: Outlook Preferred over Notes The current trend suggests the popularity of MS Outlook over other messaging client like Lotus Notes. There are several reasons that justify its dominance in the online platform. Some of them are user-friendly interface, multiple account uses based on a single connection to Exchange Server and no technical assistance. Therefore, users are shifting from Lotus Notes to Outlook, and in doing so, the NSF files stored in Lotus needs to be transferred to PST, which is a database file folder of Outlook. Converting NSF files to PST Format Now in converting the files, users must focus on few points. First-of-all, they must clear in choosing the migration process, whether to go by • Mail to Mail client migration i.e. Lotus Notes to Outlook • Server to Server Migration i.e. Domino to Exchange • Server to Mail Client Migration i.e. Domino to Outlook • Mail Client to Server Transfer i.e. Lotus Notes to Exchange Server Users can choose any of the aforementioned processes as per their requirement in order to convert their NSF files to PST. In order to convert bulk NSF files to PST, users choose the common process of Mail to Mail transfer that is (http://www.lotustooutlook.com/) Lotus Notes to Outlook along-with the database. In doing so they must make sure to select the right medium. Medium here is the way of carrying forward the migration process. Two Ways for the Way-out There are two medium through which the migration process can be done successfully. • Give a call to the IT Team • Doing it yourself by the help of third party conversion software. Which one is better? The first option of calling an IT team is not a wise decision here as it will cost bit high for end-users. In addition, the IT team will carry on with the same migration process as third party software will automatically do for users. Therefore, users are recommended to have basic know-how of these third party software tools and perform the conversion process at their own pace. This will not only save their hard-earned money but also give them the confidence of comprehending and managing the messaging platform fully for present and future operations. The question of data loss might haunt end-users as they are carrying the entire migration process single-handedly, but selecting the right and reliable conversion software can solve their every query. Convert Notes NSF to Outlook PST Users must wisely choose third party conversion software, which guarantees to (http://lotusnotesmailtooutlook.strikingly.com/) Convert NSF files to PST in a swift and fast way. The conversion software, which comes with a free demo version, should be chosen as it will help users in judging the accountability and functionality of that software before purchasing it.

Description: Canopy Gap helps organizations work courageously together.

Full Description: Vital growth requires vital interactions. Through experiences including TriLab, Interchange workshops, and a Roots of Collaboration practice, Canopy Gap helps organizations grow with vitality. We ignite customer relationships, energize teams and leaders, and activate communities. Our clients build awareness, improve relationships internally and externally, and learn how to accelerate value created throughout groups and teams. The name "Canopy Gap" comes from a phrase used in ecology referring to the open spaces in forest canopies where sunlight allows new growth to emerge on the forest floor. Gaps are dynamic phenomena that are created, sometimes expand, and usually disappear. They are essential to the well-being of the forest. Gaps create suitable conditions for rapid growth, allowing the whole ecosystem to regenerate. Likewise, leading organizations recognize that they thrive when vital interactions are flowing through the entire ecosystem.
